":"YNM","CreatedById":98447,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-09T20:10:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223951827\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201551\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221617998964\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278715\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NFUN\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, NFUN said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003Ewhat\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E????\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTank ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-10T15:16:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223951827\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201551\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221617998964\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278715\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NFUN\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, NFUN said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey flatten enemy\u0027s \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003Ewhat\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E????\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, in reality these had been just trucks, which was certainly within the bounds of the plausible. The\u00A0\u003Cem\u003ERed Star\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0began the inflation, which in turn spurred the imagination of the author of the Associated Press newswire.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-10T16:58:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003ELandkreuzer\u0027\u003C/em\u003Es are tanks. These are just tankcicles..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n***\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd what if put a compact fusion reactor on a landkreuzer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DDE","CreatedById":146349,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-10T23:08:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223952284\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022201551\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221618073924\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003ELandkreuzer\u0027\u003C/em\u003Es are tanks. These are just tankcicles..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n***\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd what if put a compact fusion reactor on a landkreuzer?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen it will just fall prey to enemy air support.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022s-c58e85ced4e8fee560433bc772f95c567f5ed2\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002278.00\u0022 height=\u0022887\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://img-s3.onedio.com/id-5af9fdfe9150bbb31c68505f/rev-0/raw/s-c58e85ced4e8fee560433bc772f95c567f5ed295.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"wumpus","CreatedById":133850,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-11T01:12:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn other news, NASA is paying BWXT ~$9.4M for one year\u0027s development of a nuclear thermal rocket.\u00A0 Granted, I\u0027m sure they are using fission, but it seems more likely than some powerpoint slides will progress quickly towards fusion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://arstechnica.com/science/2021/04/rocket-report-spacex-abandons-catching-fairings-ula-bets-on-upper-stages/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://arstechnica.com/science/2021/04/rocket-report-spacex-abandons-catching-fairings-ula-bets-on-upper-stages/\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NFUN","CreatedById":78715,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-11T02:33:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nvasimir\u0027s what you\u0027re looking for in that regard\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}